hopobject.body: We used to work together powermax sports scooters If diplomacy fails, the US must blow up its computers, cell phones, and digital cameras in its smart munitions; the US must burn millions of gallons of US gasoline, diesel fuel, and aviation fuel; and the US must waste millions of its man hours in unproductive work. Further, US bombing in the Middle East must raise the terror premium to raise the price of US gasoline to allow US drivers to send billions of US dollars to regimes in the Middle East, to al Qaeda, and to all other islamic insurgent groups. If the US chooses war in the Middle East, the US should pay for all sides in all conflicts in the Middle East.
